Privacy Policy for LocalGhost

Last Updated: [25-01-2026]

1. Data Collection LocalGhost operates entirely locally on your device. The application scans your local network to identify devices and gather technical details such as IP addresses, MAC addresses, and hostnames.

2. Data Usage The data collected is displayed solely to you within the application interface for network monitoring and forensics purposes.

3. Data Transmission LocalGhost does not transmit any of your network data, personal information, or scan results to external servers, third parties, or the publisher. All data remains strictly on your local machine.

4. Contact If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at sukheshcs@gmail.com.
